          java.lang.String directoryServerPacks

          java.util.List<E> listFallbackMods

        • listDirectoriesExclude

          java.util.List<E> listDirectoriesExclude
          List of directories which should be excluded from server packs. Default is overrides, packmenu, resourcepacks, server_pack, fancymenu.

        • curseControllerRegenerationEnabled

          boolean curseControllerRegenerationEnabled
          When running as a webservice: Whether regeneration of server packs, that have already been generated, is enabled. Default is false.

        • listCheckAgainstNewEntry

          java.util.List<E> listCheckAgainstNewEntry
          List of directories which must not be excluded from server packs. Default is mods, config, defaultconfigs, scripts, saves, seeds, libraries.

        • queueMaxDiskUsage

          int queueMaxDiskUsage
          When running as a webservice: Maximum disk usage in % at which JMS/Artemis will stop storing message in the queue saved on disk. Default is 90%.

        • saveLoadedConfiguration

          boolean saveLoadedConfiguration
          Whether the manually loaded configuration file should be saved as well as the default serverpackcreator.conf. Setting this to true will make ServerPackCreator save serverpackcreator.conf as well as the last loaded configuration-file. Default is false.

        • serverPackCreatorVersion

          java.lang.String serverPackCreatorVersion
          The version of ServerPackCreator.
          If a JAR-file compiled from a release-job from a CI/CD-pipeline is used, it should contain a VERSION.txt-file which contains the version of said release. If a non-release-version is used, from a regular pipeline or local dev-build, then this will be set to dev.

        • versioncheck_prerelease

          boolean versioncheck_prerelease
          Whether ServerPackCreator should check for available PreReleases. Set to true to get notified about available PreReleases. Set to false if you only want stable releases.

        • isCurseForgeActivated

          boolean isCurseForgeActivated
          Whether the CurseForge API in ServerPackCreator is activated. Requires a valid CurseAPI token to be set in de.griefed.serverpackcreator.curseforge.api.token.
